<h2>Welcome to <%= @user.organization.name %></h2>
<p>Hi <%= @user.name %>,</p>
<p>You've been invited to <%= @user.organization.name %>. Click the link below to sign in — no password needed. The link expires in 15 minutes and can be used once.</p>
<p><a href="<%= @url %>" style="display:inline-block;background:#2563eb;color:#fff;padding:10px 18px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;">Sign in</a></p>
<p>If you didn't expect this email, you can ignore it.</p>
<p style="color:#888;font-size:12px;">— <%= @user.organization.name %></p>
